y (parse_daily_date / day_window_for / DailyUsageQueryParams / DailyUsageResponse / DailyMetricCount validation-contract cases, including a 10-case parametrized malformed-date sweep), and 17 integration tests -- 15 in tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py (AC1-AC15 end-to-end) plus 2 in tests/integration/test_usage_rollup_rls_backstop.py (the RLS defense-in-depth backstop for AC7). Full-suite composition (pre-existing + new) totals 259 collected (255 passed, 4 skipped/deselected). This matches the plan's declared pyramid strategy: pure validation/boundary logic stayed unit, while auth/tenant-isolation/rate-limit/log/DAST/fail-closed guarantees -- only real against actual Postgres/Redis -- are integration.\",\n  \"criteria_covered\": {\n    \"total\": 15,\n    \"covered\": 15,\n    \"by_id\": [\n      { \"id\": \"AC1\", \"covered\": true, \"test\": \"tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py::test_daily_counts_aggregate_per_metric\", \"reason\": \"Seeds usage_rollup rows across two metrics, two customer_ids, and two hour-buckets on the same UTC day; asserts summed per-metric event_count in metric order.\", \"delegated\": null },\n      { \"id\": \"AC2\", \"covered\": true, \"test\": \"tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py::test_empty_day_returns_200_empty_list\", \"reason\": \"Queries a date with no events; asserts 200 with metrics == [] (never 404).\", \"delegated\": null },\n      { \"id\": \"AC3\", \"covered\": true, \"test\": \"tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py::test_missing_date_returns_400 + tests/test_schemas_usage_daily.py::test_missing_date_raises_400\", \"reason\": \"Integration wire-check plus unit test on parse_daily_date(None) both assert 400 bad_request, not 422/200.\", \"delegated\": null },\n      { \"id\": \"AC4\", \"covered\": true, \"test\": \"tests/test_schemas_usage_daily.py::test_malformed_date_raises_400 (parametrized x10) + tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py::test_malformed_date_returns_400\", \"